Package org.codehaus.janino Description

The classes in this package pose the core of the Janino JavaTM compiler.

The package comprises a scanner (Scanner, a parser (Parser) and a class file library. The parser builds a syntax tree from the "Java.*" classes that represents the parsed code. The UnitCompiler.compileUnit(org.codehaus.janino.util.enumerator.EnumeratorSet) method compiles this syntax tree into a ClassFile object, which can write JavaTM bytecode to an "OutputStream".
